text: Danish Crusade may refer to: *Danish Crusade of 1191 to Finland *Danish Crusade of 1202 to Finland, led by Anders Sunesen *Danish Crusade of 1206 to Ösel (Saaremaa), see Livonian Crusade#War against Saaremaa (1206–61) *Danish Crusade of 1219 to Estonia, see Battle of Lyndanisse
title: Danish Crusade
